The paper focuses on deep learning models and their communication protocols, which are central topics in the field of machine learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing). The paper also discusses the impact of communication on performance, which is relevant to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) and cs.SY (Systems and Control).
